This paper is primarily focused on the optimization of deep learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses parallel computing and communication constraints, which could fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The experiments involve training convolutional neural networks for image classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses exploration and optimization of local optima, which could fall under neural evolution (cs.NE) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
